Class Version

java.lang.Object
org.apache.openjpa.jdbc.meta.Version
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Strategy, VersionStrategy, MetaDataContext, MetaDataModes
public class Version extends Object implements VersionStrategy, MetaDataContext, MetaDataModes
Handles optimistic lock versioning for a class.
